width:66%; */

        font-weight: normal;
        position: relative;

  .smartBrief-signup .smartBrief-status-messages .message::before {
    font-family: "ModernPictogramsNormal";
    display: block;
    text-align: center;
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 10px;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    font-size: 2em;
    font-style: normal;
  }

    .smartBrief-signup .message-error .message {
        background: #fff;
        border-color: #e2adad;
        color: #c86161;

    .smartBrief-signup .message-success .message {
        background: #fff;
        border-color: #798e37;
        color: #6a7f2c;
    }

    .smartBrief-signup .status-loading .message::before {
        content: "`";
    }

    .smartBrief-signup .message-error .message::before {
        content: "x";
    }

    .smartBrief-signup .message-success .message::before {
        content: "%";

    .smartBrief-signup .smartBrief-status-messages.status-loading .one {
        opacity: 0;
        -webkit-animation: dot 1.3s infinite;
        -webkit-animation-delay: 0s;
        animation: dot 1.3s infinite;
        animation-delay: 0s;
    }

    .smartBrief-signup .smartBrief-status-messages.status-loading .two {
        opacity: 0;
        -webkit-animation: dot 1.3s infinite;
        -webkit-animation-delay: 0.2s;
        animation: dot 1.3s infinite;
        animation-delay: 0.2s;
    }

    .smartBrief-signup .smartBrief-status-messages.status-loading .three {
        opacity: 0;
        -webkit-animation: dot 1.3s infinite;
        -webkit-animation-delay: 0.3s;
        animation: dot 1.3s infinite;
        animation-delay: 0.3s;
    }

    .status-loading-wrapper[style*="block"] ~ .smartBrief-signup-form-wrapper
    .smartBrief-status-messages {
        display: none;
    }

    @-webkit-keyframes dot {
        0% {
